Tusaale ahaan, lymphopenia oo leh tirada unugyada cad ee dhiigga &lt; 4×109/L oo ay ku jiraan tirada lymphocyte &lt; 1×109/L, iyo heerarka sare ee aspartate aminotransferase iyo viremia ayaa laga helay 1,099 bukaan COVID-19.
