Laga soo bilaabo 6 Abriil 2020, midkoodna ma caddeyn sax ah oo ku filan in loo oggolaado isticmaalka baahsan.
Dalka Mareykanka, baaritaanka serological ee ay samaysay Cellex waxaa loo oggolaaday isticmaalka xaaladaha degdegga ah ee shaybaarro la aqoonsan yahay oo keliya.
