b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xiran dusha sare (cells membranes) ee unugyada sambabka, xididada, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirada.
ACE2 waxay ka hortagtaa dhaqdhaqaaqa angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa xaddiga angiotensin-II iyo kordhinta Ang{1-7) taasoo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daawo oo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurada wadnaha iyo xididdada dhiigga.ACE2 sidoo kale waxay u adeegtaa sida barta gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronaviruses.
Nooca bini'aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaanaa hACE2.
Angiotensin- beddelidda enzyme 2 waa zinc ay ku jiraan metloenzyme ku yaal dusha sare ee endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 protein wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa protein-ka hal-pass-ka ah ee nooca I, oo leh enzymatically domain firfircoon oo ka muuqda dusha sare ee unugyada sambabka iyo unugyada kale.
