Todobo tijaabo ayaa qiimeynayay daaweyn horay loo ansixiyay oo loogu talagalay duumada, oo ay ku jiraan afar daraasadood oo ku saabsan hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Daawooyinka ka hortagga fayraska ee dib loo isticmaalay ayaa ah inta badan cilmi baarista Shiinaha, iyadoo sagaal tijaabooyin wajiga III ah oo ku saabsan remdesivir laga sameeyay dalal badan oo la filayo in la soo gudbiyo dhammaadka Abriil.
Dib-u-eegis dhaqameed ee horumarka kiliinikada ee tallaalka COVID-19 iyo daawooyinka musharraxa ayaa la sameeyay, laga bilaabo Abriil 2020. Dhowr daawooyin oo ka hortagga fayraska ah ayaa lagu qiimeeyaa daaweynta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo lagu daray interferon beta.
