Tijaabooyinka caafimaad ee wejiga III ayaa lagu wadaa Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga. Chloroquine, oo horey loogu isticmaalay in lagu daaweeyo duumada, waxaa lagu bartay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020, natiijooyin hordhac ahna la helay.
