28 March 2020, FDA waxay soo saartay oggolaansho isticmaalka degdegga ah ee hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine si loo siiyo dhakhaatiirta daweeya dadka qaba COVID-19. Tilmaamaha daabacaadda 7aad ee Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale waxaa ku jira interferon, ribavirin ama umifenovir si loogu isticmaalo COVID-19.
Xogta hordhaca ah waxay muujineysaa in loo baahan yahay qiyaaso badan oo ribavirin ah si looga hortago SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide waxaa lagu taliyay in lagu sii wado daraasadda vivo ka dib markii la muujiyey xakameynta heerka hoose ee SARS-CoV-2. Daraasaduhu waxay muujiyeen in borotiinka ugu horeeya ee ka kooban ee ay soo saarto protease-ka transmembrane serine 2 (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay gelitaanka SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo loo marayo isdhexgalka iyada oo la marayo qaataha ACE2.
Daraasadaha chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo ay la socdaan ama aan la socon azithromycin waxay leeyihiin xaddidaadyo waaweyn oo ka hortagay bulshada caafimaadka inay qaataan daaweyntan iyada oo aan la baarin. Oseltamivir ma xakameynayo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro mana laha door la ogyahay oo ku saabsan daaweynta COVID-19.
Duufaanta cytokine waxay noqon kartaa dhibaato marxaladaha dambe ee COVID-19 ee daran.
Waxaa jira caddeyn muujinaysa in hydroxychloroquine ay yeelan karto astaamo ka hortaga duufaanka cytokine. Tocilizumab waxaa lagu daray tilmaamaha daaweynta ee Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ka dib markii daraasad yar la dhammaystiray.
Waxaa lagu sameynayaa tijaabo heer qaran ah oo heerka 2aad ah oo aan kala sooc lahayn oo Talyaaniga ah ka dib markii ay soo bandhigeen natiijooyin wanaagsan oo ku saabsan dadka qaba cudurka daran.
Marka lagu daro baaritaanka dhiigga ee loo yaqaan ' serum ferritin blood test' si loo ogaado duufaanta cytokine, waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu hormariyo horumarada noocan oo kale ah, oo loo maleynayo inay sabab u tahay dhimashada dadka qaar ee ay dhibaatadu saameysey.
Daawada loo yaqaan 'interleukin-6 receptor antagonist' waxaa ogolaaday FDA iyadoo ku saleysan daraasado kiis oo dib loo eegay oo lagu daaweynayo steroid-ka oo loo yaqaan 'cytokine-release-syndrom' oo ay keento sabab kale, CAR T cell therapy, sanadkii 2017.
Ilaa hadda, ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo la soo jeediyay, oo la xakameynayo in tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
